    + category=Fixes
        - title=Slow secure photo decryption
        - title=Crash when loading high resolution images in image editor
        - title=Crash when swiping horizontally on Favourites or Trash button in Albums View
        - title=Crash when deleting first media in an album and navigating back with Auto Detect Albums turned on
